      "manufactured_heading": "Where are Hem Healer® products manufactured?",
      "manufactured_description": "Every Hem Healer® product is proudly manufactured in the USA at an FDA-registered, GMP-certified facility in Georgia. We partner with NutraCap, a leading manufacturer known for its commitment to quality and safety. This ensures that every capsule meets the highest standards for purity and effectiveness.",
      "video_title": "Where Hem Healer is manufactured!🇺🇸 #hemorrhoids #hemorrhoidtreatment #naturalmedicine #piles",
      "results_heading": "Proven Results and Key Ingredients",
      "results_point_1": "95% of customers report success with Hem Healer®.",
      "results_point_2_prefix": "Diosmin and hesperidin, derived from citrus fruits, are clinically proven to reduce pain, bleeding, and swelling. These compounds possess strong anti-inflammatory and vascular-protective properties. ",
